entry.title: WEATHER ADVISORY , Killarney
entry.summary: Persons in or near this area should be on the lookout for adverse weather conditions and take necessary safety precautions. Issued: 06:08 AM EDT Saturday 18 March 2023

entry.title: Saturday: Flurries. High minus 3.
entry.summary: Mainly cloudy with 30 percent chance of flurries this morning. Flurries beginning late this morning. Risk of snow squalls this afternoon. Local amount 5 cm. Wind becoming west 30 km/h gusting to 50 near noon. High minus 3. Wind chill near minus 13. UV index 1 or low. Forecast issued 05:30 AM EDT Saturday 18 March 2023

entry.title: Saturday night: Flurries. Low minus 12.
entry.summary: Flurries ending after midnight then partly cloudy. Risk of snow squalls this evening. Local amount 2 cm. Wind west 30 km/h gusting to 50. Low minus 12. Wind chill minus 13 this evening and minus 20 overnight. Forecast issued 05:30 AM EDT Saturday 18 March 2023
